    <Heading Id="related" Level="2" Class="scroll-mt-20">Related Components</Heading>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm">
        <li><a href="/components/prompt-input" class="text-primary hover:underline">PromptInput</a> — Multiline AI prompt textarea with submit and keyboard shortcuts.</li>
        <li><a href="/components/reasoning-display" class="text-primary hover:underline">ReasoningDisplay</a> — Collapsible chain-of-thought block for AI reasoning traces.</li>
        <li><a href="/components/agent-message-list" class="text-primary hover:underline">AgentMessageList</a> — Chat message stream for AI agents with role-based styling.</li>
    </ul>
